<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒朝金角大王挥舞着钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你绝对不可能伤害到唐僧！”八戒大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的钉耙非常厉害！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒向金角大王冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，那妖怪十分厉害。八戒被打倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他醒过来的时候，他已经被绑在了一个漆黑的洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒去了好久。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望他没出什么事。”悟空皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他肯定又去睡觉了。我应该跟着他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还是继续走吧！”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会在路上找到八戒的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得小心点儿。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还不知道山上有没有妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人朝山上走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们听到了一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！”一个男人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人需要帮助。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们迅速跑过去，发现路上躺着一个老和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢天谢地！”老和尚说道，“请帮帮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧从马上下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一定会帮你。”他说，“请起来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我起不来了。”老和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的腿受伤了，非常疼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始哭。“我怎么回家啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要哭。”唐僧说，“我们会帮你的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的腿是怎么受伤的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有只老虎袭击了我。”老和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空怀疑地看着老和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是真的和尚。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他肯定想要伤害师父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我不能告诉师父，他不会相信我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空。”唐僧说，“你抱着这位可怜的老和尚下山吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走了过去，抱起了老和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”老和尚大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心点，悟空。”唐僧说，“他的腿伤得很重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人继续沿着路往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抱着受伤的和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走得很慢，跟在唐僧和悟净的后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是个妖怪。”悟空低声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也知道你想要吃了唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道你在说什么。”老和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是个和尚。老虎袭击了我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“你知道我是谁吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是孙悟空。我曾经打败了所有的天兵天将。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你最好不要有伤害唐僧的想法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，悟空觉得自己身上被什么重的东西压住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向上看了一眼，发现一座山正压在他的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又笑了起来。“你要用法术把我困在山下吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好吧，让我来告诉你，佛祖曾把我困在五指山下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我连那山都可以举得动。”悟空觉得更重了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，两座山压在了他的头上。他走得更慢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这重量还是无法阻止我。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，唐僧不在旁边，我要用我的金箍棒打你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那老和尚消失了。第三座山又压了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的膝盖弯曲了。三座山同时压了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空被困住了。老和尚又出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，他变回了妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金角大王开心地大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空是这一行人里最厉害的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>打败悟净会很容易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今晚我就吃了唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>